ygData.messageBody:
Hi!
Well, I'm back again although I'm not sure if anyone will even
remember me. At least this time I have EQ up and running and have
managed to figure out a few little things.

All of my toons are currently on the Xegony server where my mains are
all currently enrolled in the guild Hand of Judgement . . .
Baroness Melwen Shadowbow a High Elf Cleric of Tunare of 61 Seasons &
Brangvyne Nimloth a Wood Elf Ranger of Tunare of 52 Seasons live.
My other toons include . . .
Xenawyr - 55 Druidess
Moriel - 35 Shadow Knight
Linnathon - 33 Enchantress

Thought I would pop in and see how everyone was doing or if anyone
even remembered me etc.

If anyone plays on Xegony I would love to meet you and say hi, or if
you fall in groupable range of any of those toons to adventure a bit
together.

/Hugs to All
Bran
